Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:46.47,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我為了不讓其毀壞而太過於珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:52.39,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也輸入郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:58.26,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又將其刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:00.66,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這樣的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.83,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將其打破的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.67,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}為我帶來契機的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:11.65,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}用手心將其緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:15.23,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將現在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:18.72,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}雖然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:22.59,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使將碎片全部收集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:25.79,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也必須用自己的雙手將其指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:28.49,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}極其珍視的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:31.84,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我害怕將其失去
